column2: select s.specObjID, max (l.sigma*#/l.wave) as veldisp, avg (s.z) as z into results from SpecObj s, specLine l where s.specObjID = l.specObjID and ( (s.specClass = @qso) or (s.specClass = @hiZ_qso) ) and s.z between # and # and l.sigma*#/l.wave > # and s.zConf > # group by s.specObjID into MyDB.MyNewtable1
